    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-header">
            <span class="section-icon">🤖</span>
            AI & Tech
        </div>
        
        <div class="story">
            <div class="story-title">India AI Impact Summit kicks off TODAY</div>
            <div class="story-content">New Delhi hosts tech's biggest names — Sundar Pichai (Google), Sam Altman (OpenAI), Dario Amodei (Anthropic), Jensen Huang (Nvidia), Bill Gates, and 40+ CEOs attending. India targeting $100B investment commitments over 5 days.</div>
            <a href="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/technology/tech-news/india-ai-impact-summit-2026-sundar-pichai-sam-altman-dario-amodei-and-full-list-of-ceos-attending-the-summit-in-delhi/articleshow/128373872.cms" class="story-link">Times of India</a>
        </div>

        <div class="story">
            <div class="story-title">Software companies frantically rebranding as "AI companies"</div>
            <div class="story-content">Stocks plunge 20% in past month, wiping out $2T in market cap. "Sparkles emojis and magic wand icons are everywhere" as companies pivot amid existential crisis.</div>
            <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/14/business/dealbook/software-companies-ai.html" class="story-link">New York Times</a>
        </div>

        <div class="story">
            <div class="story-title">Elon Musk's Grok gaining US market share</div>
            <div class="story-content">Up to 17.8% from 14% in December amid ongoing image generation controversies.</div>
            <a href="https://startupnews.fyi/2026/02/15/elon-musks-ai-chatbot-grok-gains-us-market-share-amid-sexualised-images-backlash-data-shows/" class="story-link">StartupNews.fyi</a>
        </div>
    </div>

